Class InternshipFilterSettings

java.lang.Object
sc2002OOP.obj.InternshipFilterSettings
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class InternshipFilterSettings extends Object implements Serializable

Internship Filter Settings (Data Structure)

This class serves as a container for all potential search criteria applicable to internship opportunities. It is primarily used to store the filter settings provided by users when they view the available internships.

Version:
1.0
Author:
Kee Kai Wen, Kelvin Tay Wei Jie, Koay Jun Zhi, Lim Jia Wei Jerald, Teo Kai Jie
